{{vgname|傳送門2|en=Portal 2}}是一款由[[威尔乌|维尔福]]開發及發行的[[第一人稱視角遊戲|第一人稱]][[益智遊戲|解謎遊戲]]，是2007年遊戲《[[傳送門|傳送門]]》（{{lang-en|''Portal''}}）的續作。游戏于2011年4月19日在[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[Mac_OS_X|Mac OS X]]、[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]以及[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]平台发布。零售版本由[[美国艺电|美国艺电]]发行，而Windows、[[Linux|Linux]]以及OS X的可下载版本由维尔福自家的游戏分发系统[[Steam|Steam]]发行。內含《傳送門》與《傳送門2》的《傳送門：同伴合集》預定於2022年內在[[任天堂Switch|任天堂Switch]]平台推出<ref name="switch">{{cite news |author1=RU |title=集結《傳送門》一、二代的《傳送門：同伴合集》今年將在 Switch 平台上市 |url=https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=227745 |accessdate=2022-02-13 |publisher=[[巴哈姆特電玩資訊站|巴哈姆特電玩資訊站]] |date=2022-02-10 |archive-date=2022-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220216102851/https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=227745 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2010年3月，《传送门》发布更新，稍微修改了游戏的结局，以此来表示续作的制作。2010年3月5日，维尔福宣布将开发《传送门2》。在游戏正式发布之前，维尔福推出了内含13款独立游戏的[[另类实境游戏|另类实境游戏]]《[[Potato_Sack|馬鈴薯袋]]》，让玩家以为可以-{zh-cn:通过;zh-tw:透過;}-[[分布式计算|-{zh-cn:分布式计算;zh-tw:分散式運算;}-]]的形式来让游戏提前几个小时发布。

《传送门2》保留了前作的大部分游戏元素，并添加了许多新元素，例如强光桥、高热能激光、凝胶等。其中凝胶的创意来自2009年[[独立游戏节|独立游戏节]]最佳学生游戏——[[迪吉彭理工學院|迪吉彭理工學院]]学生制作的《{{tsl|en|Tag: The Power of Paint|标签：油漆的力量}}》。《传送门2》包括单人模式和合作模式。单人模式的主角仍为前作的{{le|雪儿 (传送门)|Chell (Portal)|雪儿}}（{{lang-en|Chell}}）。游戏以主角在休眠设施中深度睡眠了若干年之后被唤醒开始，主角需要在荒废的光圈科学设施中与被重新激活的人工智能体GLaDOS重建科学。另外单人模式有多名新角色登场，例如{{le|惠特利|Wheatley (Portal)}}（{{lang-en|Wheatley}}，[[斯蒂芬·默切特|斯蒂芬·默切特]]配音）、{{le|卡夫·強森|Cave Johnson (Portal)}}（{{lang-en|Cave Johnson}}，或译为“凯文·约翰逊”{{efn|虽然《传送门2》为官方中文化游戏，但在游戏中各角色名字均采用英文。}}，[[J·K·西蒙斯|J·K·西蒙斯]]配音）等。合作模式的主角是叫做Atlas和P-Body的两个机器人，它们需要-{zh-cn:通过; zh-tw:透過}-合作来解决一系列谜题。

在游戏发布之后，维尔福又推出了《传送门2》的更新，包括额外的[[追加下載內容|追加下載內容]]、简化版的地图编辑器等。-{zh-cn:通过;zh-tw:透過;}-Steam的“创意工坊”，玩家可以将自己设计的关卡发布到-{zh-cn:社区;zh-tw:社群;}-，或者下载来自-{zh-cn:社区;zh-tw:社群;}-的关卡。

一些评论认为将《传送门》拓展成完整系列的难度较大，但是大多数评论都对《传送门2》持好评。游戏的创作、节奏以及[[黑色幽默|黑色幽默]]都是极为突出的亮点，其配音受到了一些媒体的好评，游戏的新元素、渐进的挑战和附加的合作模式都受到称赞。多个媒体将《传送门2》列为2011年年度游戏之一，以及{{tsl|en|List of video games considered the best|被评为最好的电子游戏列表|史上最佳电子游戏之一}}。

== 玩法 ==
{{see also|傳送門#玩法}}
[[File:Portal_physics-2.svg|left]]
與前作《傳送門》一樣，玩家在單人模式要以[[第一人称射击游戏|第一人稱視角]]控制一名叫做{{le|雪儿 (传送门)|Chell (Portal)|雪儿}}的女性角色，在合作模式需要控制两个机器人Atlas和P-body中的一个，在自定义地图则是控制一个人形的图标。他們都是典型的沉默主角，因此玩家不会听到自己所控制的角色说话。主角可以承受少量伤害，但是受到持续伤害之后会死亡。主角不会受到坠落伤害，不过若是落入无底洞或毒性液体中会立刻死亡。在单人模式中，一旦雪儿死亡，游戏会重新回到最近的[[游戏存档|游戏存档]]<ref name="gi reveal" />；在合作模式中，如果机器人死亡，游戏会照常进行，而角色会立刻重生<ref name="pcworld interview" />。游戏发生在光圈科技的设施——复杂可变的机械迷宫之中。大多数时间玩家会处于模块化的“实验室”内，实验室内会有明确的入口和出口。玩家需要解开实验室所布置的谜题，达到出口并离开实验室。另外游戏也有一些彩蛋，玩家也可以进入到幕后区域<ref>{{Cite web|title=Portal 2 Secrets Guide|url=https://www.pcgamer.com/portal-2-secrets-guide/|accessdate=2020-02-24|date=2011-04-24|last=Purslow|first=Matt|work=PC Gamer|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201214141052/https://www.pcgamer.com/portal-2-secrets-guide/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

游戏初期会有一些教学性质的关卡，引导玩家学会基本的控制和交互方法。玩家必须使用「光圈科學手持傳送門裝置」（簡稱「傳送門槍」）解决谜题。该装置可以在白色墙面上建立两种颜色的传送门。这两种传送门沒有特定分何者為入口、何者為出口，而且互相连通。任何物體（包括玩家）在穿過其中一道傳送門後，就會穿越另一道傳送門到達不同地點。玩家可以通过传送门进行移动，或“抛掷”自己或一个物体。无论是在墙面，还是被障碍物遮挡，传送门的轮廓都是可见的，这样可便于定位<ref name="cvg edge l4d">{{cite web | url = http://www.computerandvideogames.com/288474/news/portal-2-influenced-by-left-4-dead-valve/ | title = Portal 2 influenced by Left 4 Dead – Valve | work = [[电脑与电子游戏|Computer and Video Games]] | date = 2011-02-11 | accessdate = 2011-02-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110213144938/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/288474/news/portal-2-influenced-by-left-4-dead-valve/ | archive-date = 2011-02-13 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="telegraph interview">{{cite news | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/video-games/8359173/Portal-2-developer-interview-Chet-Falisek-and-Erik-Wolpaw.html | title = Portal 2 developer interview: Chet Falisek and Erik Wolpaw | work = [[每日电讯报|The Daily Telegraph]] | date = 2011-03-04 | accessdate = 2011-03-04 | first = David | last = Brown | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110309212313/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/video-games/8359173/Portal-2-developer-interview-Chet-Falisek-and-Erik-Wolpaw.html | archive-date = 2011-03-09 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

游戏引入了一些新的游戏元素。例如，高热能激光可以与接收器配合充当开关，也可摧毁炮塔；传送隧道可以吸引或推动玩家与物体；强光桥可以为玩家提供一个站立与行走的桥面。这些游戏元素均能穿过传送门<ref name="gi reveal" /><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.computerandvideogames.com/253854/news/two-more-portal-2-e3-gameplay-videos/ | title = Two more Portal 2 E3 gameplay videos | first = Mike | last = Jackson | date = 2010-06-29 | accessdate =2010-07-01 | publisher = [[电脑与电子游戏|Computer and Video Games]]}}</ref><ref name="g4tv pax">{{cite web | url = http://g4tv.com/games/xbox-360/63787/portal-2/articles/72045/PAX-Prime-2010-Portal-2-Co-Op-Hands-On-Impressions/ | title = PAX Prime 2010: Portal 2 Co-Op Hands-On Impressions | first = Stephen | last = Johnson | date = 2010-09-03 | accessdate = 2010-09-03 | publisher = [[G4_(电视频道)|G4 (电视频道)]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120115024905/http://www.g4tv.com/games/xbox-360/63787/portal-2/articles/72045/PAX-Prime-2010-Portal-2-Co-Op-Hands-On-Impressions/ | archive-date = 2012-01-15 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="ign pax">{{cite web | url = http://xbox360.ign.com/articles/111/1118382p1.html | title = Portal 2 Multiplayer Preview | first = Arthur | last = Gies | date = 2010-09-06 | accessdate = 2010-09-06 | publisher = IGN | archivedate = 2012-01-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120125084337/http://xbox360.ign.com/articles/111/1118382p1.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。另外，空中弹射板可以把玩家或物体抛到指定位置；机枪炮塔会对玩家射击，所以玩家需要阻止炮塔工作或避免进入炮塔的视线。前作的重量存储方块经过重新设计，分化出了可以改变激光方向的折射方块、没有边框的球、20世纪风格的方块和由游戏角色惠特利制造的机枪炮塔方块（又被称为“Frankenturret”）<ref name="gi reveal" /><ref name="shacknews demo 4 5" />。心形装饰的同伴方块也重新出现<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.pcgamer.com/2011/03/01/12-new-high-res-portal-2-screenshots-confirm-companion-cube-comeback/ | title = 12 new high-res Portal 2 screenshots confirm Companion Cube comeback | first = Tom | last = Senior | date = 2011-02-28 | accessdate = 2011-03-01 | work = [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] | archivedate = 2011-11-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111124175600/http://www.pcgamer.com/2011/03/01/12-new-high-res-portal-2-screenshots-confirm-companion-cube-comeback | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在早期的演示版本中，游戏还包括能够传送物体与产生吸引力的通风管等，但这些元素最终并未在正式版本中出现<ref name="gi reveal" /><ref name="shacknews demo 4 5">{{cite web | url = http://www.shacknews.com/article/64559/portal-2-e3-demo-videos | title = Portal 2 E3 Demo Videos Part 4 and Part 5 Incite Anger | first = Xas | last = de Matos | date = 2010-06-30 | accessdate = 2010-07-01 | publisher = [[Shacknews|Shacknews]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110614155855/http://www.shacknews.com/article/64559/portal-2-e3-demo-videos | archive-date = 2011-06-14 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="final hours">{{Cite book | asin = B004XMZZKQ | title = The Final Hours of Portal 2 | first = Geoff | last = Keighley | year = 2011}} Also available as iPad or Steam application.</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://multiplayerblog.mtv.com/2011/04/29/behold-some-amazing-portal-2-cube-tricks/ | title = Behold Some Amazing 'Portal 2' Cube Tricks | first = Russ | last = Frushtick | date = 2011-04-29 | accessdate = 2011-04-29 | publisher = MTV | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110501011034/http://multiplayerblog.mtv.com/2011/04/29/behold-some-amazing-portal-2-cube-tricks/ | archivedate = 2011-05-01 }}</ref>。所有的游戏元素都与解谜有关，它们会帮助或妨碍玩家完成谜题。<ref>{{Cite web|title=大众软件：透析《传送门2》的乐趣宝库_单机游戏_新浪游戏_新浪网|url=http://games.sina.com.cn/j/n/2011-08-24/1120524895.shtml|accessdate=2020-02-24|work=games.sina.com.cn|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807193422/http://games.sina.com.cn/j/n/2011-08-24/1120524895.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

游戏还引入了几种凝胶。凝胶从游戏内的管道喷出，可通过传送门传送。凝胶在附着物体或墙面之后会产生特定的效果<ref name="gi reveal" />。蓝色的排斥凝胶可以使主角跳得更高，橙色的推进凝胶可以使主角跑得更快<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.vg247.com/2010/07/01/portal-2-e3-demo-final-parts-6-7-out-now/ | title = Portal 2 E3 demo: final parts 6 and 7 out now | first = Stephany | last = Nunneley | date = 2010-07-01 | accessdate = 2010-07-01 | publisher = [[VG247|VG247]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100704114551/http://www.vg247.com/2010/07/01/portal-2-e3-demo-final-parts-6-7-out-now/ | archive-date = 2010-07-04 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。白色的转换凝胶可以使玩家在它的表面上建立传送门<ref name="telegraph review">{{cite news | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/video-games/8458871/Portal-2-review.html | title = Portal 2 Review | date = 2011-04-19 | accessdate = 2011-04-19 | work = [[每日电讯报|The Daily Telegraph]] | first = Tom | last = Hoggins | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110419151249/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/video-games/8458871/Portal-2-review.html | archive-date = 2011-04-19 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

游戏包括双人合作模式<ref name="p2_coop_confirmed">{{cite web | url = http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2010/03/05/portal-2-for-two.aspx | title = Portal 2 For Two | work = [[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] | first = Annette | last = Gonzalez | date = 2010-03-05 | accessdate = 2010-03-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100307064210/http://gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2010/03/05/Portal-2-For-Two.aspx | archive-date = 2010-03-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。两个玩家既可以以同一主机分屏显示的形式进行游戏，也可以使用各自的电脑或游戏机。Windows、Mac OS X和PlayStation 3平台的玩家可以互相连接而无需考虑对方的平台。2012年下半年维尔福发布补丁，为Windows和Mac平台玩家加入了分屏支持<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.vg247.com/2012/11/21/portal-2-update-adds-big-picture-split-screen/ | title = Portal 2 update adds Big Picture split-screen | first = Brenna | last = Hillier | date = 2012-11-21 | accessdate = 2012-11-21 | publisher = [[VG247|VG247]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121128191017/http://www.vg247.com/2012/11/21/portal-2-update-adds-big-picture-split-screen/ | archive-date = 2012-11-28 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。两位玩家需要操作的角色都是机器人，二者均拥有自己的传送门枪，并且每个角色都可以进入对方设置的传送门<ref name="gi reveal" />。两位玩家建立的传送门采用不同的配色方案，其中一个是蓝色和紫色，另外一个是橙色和红色<ref name="ign pax" /><ref name="ign e3" />。一开始会有一个校准实验室来指导玩家如何使用传送门和沟通工具。大多数实验室会要求玩家各自设置传送门来重定向激光、重定向传送隧道、发射物体或做出其他动作等<ref name="usatoday coop">{{cite news | url = http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gamehunters/post/2011/04/portal-2-a-closer-look-at-cooperative-play/1 | title = 'Portal 2': A closer look at co-operative play | first = Brett | last = Molina | date = 2011-04-19 | accessdate = 2011-04-20 | work = [[今日美國|USA Today]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110426065822/http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gamehunters/post/2011/04/portal-2-a-closer-look-at-cooperative-play/1 | archive-date = 2011-04-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。游戏提供了语音交流功能。玩家也可以随时进入分屏视角来协助与指导对方<ref name="ign e3">{{cite web | url = http://ps3.ign.com/articles/109/1098375p1.html | title = E3 2010: Portal 2 Preview | first = Damien | last = Hatfield | date = 2010-06-16 | accessdate = 2010-06-16 | publisher = IGN | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100618200728/http://ps3.ign.com/articles/109/1098375p1.html | archive-date = 2010-06-18 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。玩家可-{zh-cn:通过; zh-tw:透過}-一个名为“Ping”的工具来标记物体或墙面的位置、启动倒计时来同时做某一动作。玩家之间也可以互相打手势，例如挥手或拥抱等<ref name="gi reveal" /><ref name="g4tv pax" /><ref name="usatoday coop" />。游戏会记录玩家通过的实验室，在玩家与新的伙伴合作时允许玩家重玩那些实验室。

《传送门2》编剧{{le|艾瑞克·沃保|Erik Wolpaw}}估计游戏需要大约6小时来完成<ref name="pcworld interview">{{cite web | url = http://www.pcgamer.com/2010/09/10/interview-valve-on-their-insane-portal-2-ideas/ | title = Interview: Valve on their insane Portal 2 ideas | first = Tom | last = Francis | work = PC World | date = 2010-09-10 | accessdate = 2010-09-10 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/663R4AQA2?url=http://www.pcgamer.com/2010/09/10/interview-valve-on-their-insane-portal-2-ideas/ | archive-date = 2012-03-10 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。游戏包括“开发者注释”功能，玩家-{zh-cn:通关;zh-tw:破關;}-之后可以开启此模式。在开发者注释模式中，游戏内会有一些表示注释的图标，玩家可对其按下使用键，以听取开发者、编剧、美术等游戏工作人员的评论<ref name="gamasutra johnson interview">{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/6198/rewarding_the_players_valve_on_.php | title = Rewarding The Players: Valve On Portal 2 | first = Brandon | last = Sheffield | date = 2010-11-08 | accessdate = 2010-11-10 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101110010451/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/6198/rewarding_the_players_valve_on_.php | archive-date = 2010-11-10 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。按照维尔福的说法，单人模式和合作模式每关长度都是前作《传送门》的2到2.5倍，而總長度則是前作的5倍<ref name="telegraph interview">{{cite news | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/video-games/8359173/Portal-2-developer-interview-Chet-Falisek-and-Erik-Wolpaw.html | title = Portal 2 developer interview: Chet Falisek and Erik Wolpaw | work = [[每日电讯报|The Daily Telegraph]] | date = 2011-03-04 | accessdate = 2011-03-04 | first = David | last = Brown | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110309212313/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/technology/video-games/8359173/Portal-2-developer-interview-Chet-Falisek-and-Erik-Wolpaw.html | archive-date = 2011-03-09 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="g4tv pax" /><ref>{{cite web | url = http://technolog.msnbc.msn.com/_news/2010/09/08/5068274-dear-valve-portal-2-better-be-awesome-but-no-pressure | title = Dear Valve, 'Portal 2' better be awesome. But no pressure. | first = Winda | last = Benedetti | date = 2010-09-08 | accessdate = 2010-09-08 | publisher = [[MSNBC|MSNBC]] | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100910233151/http://technolog.msnbc.msn.com/_news/2010/09/08/5068274-dear-valve-portal-2-better-be-awesome-but-no-pressure | archivedate = 2010-09-10 }}</ref>。

