ccessdate = 2011-04-19 | work = {{tsl|en|Paste Magazine||Paste Magazine}} | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110424044748/http://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2011/04/the-national-release-exile-vilify-off-portal-2-sou.html | archive-date = 2011-04-24 | dead-url = no }}</ref>游戏内的大多数音乐被制作成三部专辑《Songs to Test By》，从2011年5月开始玩家可以免费下载<ref name="soundtrack">{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-05-25-valve-offers-portal-2-soundtrack-for-free|title=Valve offers Portal 2 soundtrack for free|date=2011-05-25|accessdate=2011-05-25|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|first=Fred|last=Dutton|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110528150855/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-05-25-valve-offers-portal-2-soundtrack-for-free|archive-date=2011-05-28|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="eurog peer review"/>。后来该专辑于2012年10月发行零售版本，其中包含了前作《传送门》的音轨<ref>{{Cite journal | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-09-25-portal-2-songs-to-test-by-collectors-edition-due-next-month | title = Portal 2: Songs To Test By (Collector's Edition) due next month | first = Jeffrey | last = Matulef | date = 2012-09-25 | accessdate = 2012-12-23 | publisher = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | journal =  | author =  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130102185636/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2012-09-25-portal-2-songs-to-test-by-collectors-edition-due-next-month | archive-date = 2013-01-02 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

