2008年1月，维尔福发言人道格·隆巴尔迪（Doug Lombardi）向[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]透露，“我们保证一定会有更多的《传送门》”<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/more-portal-for-sure-valve |title = ''More Portal for sure'' – Valve |accessdate = 2008-01-30 |author = Purchese, Rob |date = 2008-01-31 |publisher = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/663RVFKZv?url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/more-portal-for-sure-valve |archive-date = 2012-03-10 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。《传送门》设计师{{le|金·斯威夫特|Kim Swift}}确认《传送门2》的开发工作会从下个月开始<ref>{{cite episode | title = Portal | url = http://www.g4tv.com/videos/20385/face-time-portal/ | series = Face Time | network = G4TV | airdate = 2008-02-21 | accessdate = 2011-06-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121017131242/http://www.g4tv.com/videos/20385/face-time-portal/ | archive-date = 2012-10-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。斯威夫特说，开发《传送门》的多人模式在技术上可行<ref>{{cite episode |title=Valve Releases the Pressure |series=GT.TV with Geoff Keighley |network=[[GameTrailers|GameTrailers]] |url=http://www.gametrailers.com/episode/gametrailers-tv/10&ch=2&sd=1?ep=10&ch=2&sd=1 |airdate=2008-03-01 |accessdate=2011-06-26 |archivedate=2010-12-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101231000714/http://www.gametrailers.com/episode/gametrailers-tv/10%26ch%3D2%26sd%3D1?ep=10&ch=2&sd=1 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，但是“没有你想的那样有趣”<ref name="shacknews gdc08 interview">{{cite web | url = http://www.shacknews.com/article/51474/gdc-08-portal-creators-on | title = GDC 08: Portal Creators on Writing, Multiplayer, Government Interrogation Techniques | publisher = Shacknews | date = 2008-02-23 | accessdate = 2008-02-23 | first = Chris | last = Faylor | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110424104647/http://www.shacknews.com/article/51474/gdc-08-portal-creators-on | archive-date = 2011-04-24 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

维尔福于2010年3月5日-{zh-cn:通过; zh-tw:透過}-《[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]》杂志正式宣布将要推出《传送门2》。不过之前一周内发生的事情已经预示了这一点：3月1日，维尔福发布了《传送门》的补丁，在其中加入了一个新成就“Transmission Received”，要求玩家将游戏内的收音机放到指定位置。放置收音机产生的音效成为了[[另類實境遊戲|另類實境遊戲]]的一个环节<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.pcworld.com/article/195026/anatomy_of_an_alternatereality_game.html | title = Anatomy of an Alternate-Reality Game | date = 2010-04-26 | accessdate = 2010-05-13 | publisher = [[GamePro|GamePro]] | first = Alex | last = Wawro | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100501031529/http://www.pcworld.com/article/195026/anatomy_of_an_alternatereality_game.html | archive-date = 2010-05-01 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。新的效果包括暗示GLaDOS将要重启的[[摩尔斯电码|摩尔斯电码]]和来自光圈科技视频的[[慢扫描电视|慢扫描电视]]图像。一个神秘的电话号码连接到了一个[[BBS|BBS]]系统，其数据包括一些与《传送门》和光圈科技档案相关的[[ASCII艺术|ASCII图像]]。它们都在暗示一些事情<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.shacknews.com/article/62575/portal-patch-adds-morse-code | title = Portal Patch Adds Morse Code, Achievement – Portal 2 Speculation Begins (Updated) | first1 = Alice | last1 = O'Connor | first2 = Brian | last2 = Leahy | date = 2010-03-01 | accessdate = 2010-03-02 | publisher = [[Shacknews|Shacknews]] | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/69i908c8o?url=http://www.shacknews.com/article/62575/portal-patch-adds-morse-code | archive-date = 2012-08-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。多数ASCII图像随后被《Game Informer》杂志披露出来<ref name="gi reveal" />。在维尔福正式宣布将要推出游戏之后，新的ASCII图片继续流露出来。另类实境游戏的背景被嵌入在额外的一张慢扫描电视图像中，可以在《传送门2》的一个隐藏房间内找到<ref name="arg p2 room">{{cite web | url = http://www.joystiq.com/2011/04/19/portal-2-easter-egg-valve-never-meta-arg-it-didnt-like/ | title = Portal 2 Easter egg: Valve never meta-ARG it didn't like | first = JC | last = Fletcher | date = 2011-04-20 | accessdate = 2011-04-20 | publisher = Joystiq | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110423032325/http://www.joystiq.com/2011/04/19/portal-2-easter-egg-valve-never-meta-arg-it-didnt-like/ | archive-date = 2011-04-23 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。另类实境游戏的想法由维尔福员工亚当·福斯特（Adam Foster）提出。他与公司在《Game Informer》透风的行动紧密配合。他通过自己家中的电话线路来运行[[BBS|BBS]]软件，因为维尔福办公室的设备太新，不支持相关的传输协议。福斯特估计这个另类实境游戏需要花费不到100美元<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-06-04-the-first-anyone-had-seen-publicly-of-portal-2-was-relayed-over-this-modem-from-1987-from-my-kitchen | title = The first anyone had seen publicly of Portal 2 was relayed over this modem from 1987 from my kitchen | first = Robert | last = Purchase | date = 2013-06-07 | accessdate = 2013-06-07 | publisher = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130610172809/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-06-04-the-first-anyone-had-seen-publicly-of-portal-2-was-relayed-over-this-modem-from-1987-from-my-kitchen | archive-date = 2013-06-10 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/blogs/AdamFoster/20130617/194321/ | title = Alternate Reality Game puzzle design | first = Adam | last = Foster | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | date = 2013-06-18 | accessdate = 2013-06-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130701161614/http://www.gamasutra.com/blogs/AdamFoster/20130617/194321/ | archive-date = 2013-07-01 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

[[File:Gdc2010_newell_portal_BSOD.jpg|right]]，[[加布·纽维尔|加布·纽维尔]]和GLaDOS版[[藍屏死機|藍屏死機]]畫面|alt=加布·纽维尔站在大屏幕前面，屏幕類似Windows作業系統的藍屏死機，但是文字有所不同，內含詞語「GLaDOS」。]]

3月3日，《传送门》发布第二个补丁，游戏结局改为雪儿被拖回了光圈科技设施中<ref name="shacknews update 2">{{cite web | url = http://www.shacknews.com/article/62622/valve-changes-portals-ending-in | title = Portal Mystery Deepens with Second Update | first = Chris | last = Faylor | date = 2010-03-03 | accessdate = 2010-03-03 | publisher = [[Shacknews|Shacknews]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110320032144/http://www.shacknews.com/article/62622/valve-changes-portals-ending-in | archive-date = 2011-03-20 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。游戏网站编者们预测，维尔福很快就会宣布《传送门2》<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2010/03/portal-viral/ | title = Geeky Clues Suggest Portal Sequel Is Coming | work = [[连线|Wired]] | first = Gus | last = Mastrapa | date = 2010-03-02 | accessdate = 2010-03-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100303235223/http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2010/03/portal-viral/ | archive-date = 2010-03-03 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.g4tv.com/thefeed/blog/post/702963/rumor-valve-to-make-portal-2-announcement-during-gdc-2010/ | title = Rumor: Valve To Make Portal 2 Announcement During GDC 2010 | work = {{tsl|en|X-Play||X-Play}} | date = 2010-03-03 | accessdate = 2010-03-03 | first = Jake | last = Gaskill | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121017172010/http://www.g4tv.com/thefeed/blog/post/702963/rumor-valve-to-make-portal-2-announcement-during-gdc-2010/ | archive-date = 2012-10-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。3月5日，《[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]》指出他们将在四月发行的杂志中宣布《传送门2》的正式发行<ref>{{cite web | url = http://arstechnica.com/gaming/news/2010/03/portal-2-is-official-first-image-inside.ars | title = Portal 2 is official, first image inside | date = 2010-03-05 | accessdate = 2010-03-05 | first = Andrew | last = Webster | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100307124459/http://arstechnica.com/gaming/news/2010/03/portal-2-is-official-first-image-inside.ars | archive-date = 2010-03-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。接下来的一周，加布·纽维尔参加了2010年[[游戏开发者大会|游戏开发者大会]]，接受[[游戏开发者选择奖|游戏先驱奖]]并发表了演讲，演讲以展示[[蓝屏死机|蓝屏死机]]画面的形式结束。从画面中可以看到，消息来自GLaDOS，以此暗示2010年[[E3电子娱乐展|E3]]大会时会有更多关于《传送门2》的消息<ref>{{cite web | url = http://kotaku.com/5491651/portal-2-hijacks-blue-screen-of-death-at-gdc-awards | title = Portal 2 Hijacks Blue Screen of Death At GDC Awards | first = Luke | last = Plunkett | date = 2010-03-11 | accessdate = 2010-03-12 | publisher = Kotaku | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100314003729/http://kotaku.com/5491651/portal-2-hijacks-blue-screen-of-death-at-gdc-awards | archive-date = 2010-03-14 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在E3大会两星期之前，游戏网站编者们收到了一封由光圈科技发布的、内容隐晦的邮件，暗示《传送门2》的展示会被换成一个“惊喜”。这引发了人们对“惊喜”内容的推测。人们感觉可能是《[[半衰期2：第三章|半衰期2：第三章]]》<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/e3-portal-2-event-replaced-by-surprise | title = E3 Portal 2 event replaced by "surprise" | first = Robert | last = Purchase | date = 2010-06-02 | accessdate = 2010-06-02 | publisher = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100605022850/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/e3-portal-2-event-replaced-by-surprise | archive-date = 2010-06-05 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，不过维尔福指出那个“惊喜”是关于《传送门2》的<ref name="shack delay">{{cite web | url = http://www.shacknews.com/article/64185/valve-delays-portal-2-confirms | title = Valve Delays Portal 2, Confirms E3 Surprise Is 'PORTAL-2-THEMED-FOR-GOD'S SAKE' | publisher = [[Shacknews|Shacknews]] | date = 2010-06-09 | accessdate = 2010-06-09 | first = Chris | last = Faylor | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110409164713/http://www.shacknews.com/article/64185/valve-delays-portal-2-confirms | archive-date = 2011-04-09 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。实际上，那个“惊喜”是《传送门2》将要推出[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]版<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.pcgamer.com/2010/06/15/valves-e3-surprise-is-oh-portal-2-on-ps3/ | title = Valve’s E3 surprise is... oh. Portal 2 on PS3 | first = Tom | last = Francis | publisher = PC Gamer | date = 2010-06-15 | accessdate = 2011-06-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110426215821/http://www.pcgamer.com/2010/06/15/valves-e3-surprise-is-oh-portal-2-on-ps3/ | archive-date = 2011-04-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 营销和发布 ===
维尔福最初宣布将于2010年下半年正式发布《传送门2》<ref name="gi reveal">{{cite news|title=Portal 2|first=Meagan|last=VanBurkleo|date=April 2010|pages=50–62|work=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]}}</ref><ref name="xmas" />。2010年8月，维尔福将游戏正式发布时间推迟到了2011年2月，Steam版发布时间推迟到了2011年2月9日<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/102867-Portal-2-Teleports-to-Shelves-Next-February | title = Portal 2 Teleports to Shelves Next February | first = Gregory | last = Gay | date = 2010-08-18 | accessdate = 2011-04-21 | publisher = {{tsl|en|Escapist (magazine)||Escapist}} | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100821232135/http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/102867-Portal-2-Teleports-to-Shelves-Next-February | archive-date = 2010-08-21 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，以便完善游戏对话、实验室和凝胶等游戏内容的设计<ref name="final hours"/>。2010年10月，维尔福再次将游戏正式发布时间推迟到2011年4月18日。全球范围内零售版本和线上版本都会于这一天发布<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.shacknews.com/article/66536/portal-2-delayed-hits-stores|title=Portal 2 Delayed to 'The Week of April 18'|first=Xav|last=de Matos|publisher=[[Shacknews|Shacknews]]|date=2010-11-18|accessdate=2010-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110307032034/http://www.shacknews.com/article/66536/portal-2-delayed-hits-stores|archive-date=2011-03-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。艾瑞克·沃保说推迟八个星期是为了在“内容锁定”（在开发过程中达到某个阶段之后就不再加入新内容）之前丰富游戏的内容。剩下的开发工作还包括程序调试等。加布·纽维尔认为公司不能因为产品缺少某些内容而错失良机，于是批准了推迟发布<ref name="develop valve interview"/>。2011年2月18日，加布·纽维尔确认《传送门2》的开发工作已经完成，团队正在“等待最终批准发布，并且开始着手生产盘片”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.computerandvideogames.com/289822/news/newell-portal-2-pretty-much-ready-for-release/ | title = Newell: Portal 2 'pretty much' ready for release | date = 2011-02-19 | accessdate = 2011-02-20 | work = [[电脑与电子游戏|Computer and Video Games]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110222165443/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/289822/news/newell-portal-2-pretty-much-ready-for-release/ | archive-date = 2011-02-22 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。《传送门2》是维尔福在[[Steam|Steam]]平台上发布的第一个同时支持Windows和Mac系统的游戏<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.shacknews.com/article/62687/steam-coming-to-mac-in | title = Steam Coming to Mac in April, Portal 2 This Fall | publisher = [[Shacknews|Shacknews]] | first = Chris | last = Faylor | date = 2010-03-08 | accessdate = 2010-03-08 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/663WciFVl?url=http://www.shacknews.com/article/62687/steam-coming-to-mac-in | archive-date = 2012-03-10 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。各平台的零售版本均由[[美国艺电|美国艺电]]发行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/32162/EA_Valve_Confirm_Distribution_Agreement_For_Portal_2.php|title=EA, Valve Confirm Distribution Agreement For Portal 2|first=Kris|last=Graff|date=2010-12-22|accessdate=2010-12-22|publisher=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101225133128/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/32162/EA_Valve_Confirm_Distribution_Agreement_For_Portal_2.php|archive-date=2010-12-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

{{double image|right|Portal 2 ad on a King County Metro bus in Bellevue, WA.jpg|120|Portal 2 (double-deck) bus ad.jpg|135|公共汽车上的《传送门2》广告，分别摄于美国[[西雅图|西雅图]]和英国[[利兹|利兹]]。}}

2011年4月1日，维尔福发布了另一款另类实境游戏《{{tsl|en|Potato Sack|马铃薯袋}}》<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.next-gen.biz/news/potato-sack-developers-helped-design-portal-2-arg | title = Potato Sack Developers Helped Design Portal 2 ARG | work = [[Edge_(杂志)|Edge]] | date = 2011-04-20 | accessdate = 2011-04-20 | first = Nathan | last = Brown | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110423010511/http://www.next-gen.biz/news/potato-sack-developers-helped-design-portal-2-arg | archivedate = 2011-04-23 }}</ref>。玩家们试图解决多层次的谜题，借助网站和聊天室互相协调。一些记者相信这款游戏意味着《传送门2》将提前到4月15日发布，而非原先计划的19日<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.metro.co.uk/tech/games/860768-portal-2-to-get-early-release-on-steam | title = Portal 2 to get early release on Steam? | date = 2011-04-13 | accessdate = 2011-04-13 | first = Tom | last = Phillips | work = {{tsl|en|Metro (British newspaper)||The Metro}} | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110417014518/http://www.metro.co.uk/tech/games/860768-portal-2-to-get-early-release-on-steam | archive-date = 2011-04-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.vg247.com/2011/04/13/portal-2-to-release-early-potato-sack-arg-signs-point-to-yes/ | title = Portal 2 to release early? Potato sack ARG signs point to "yes" | first = Nathan | last = Greyson | date = 2011-04-13 | accessdate = 2011-04-13 | publisher = [[VG247|VG247]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110416054113/http://www.vg247.com/2011/04/13/portal-2-to-release-early-potato-sack-arg-signs-point-to-yes/ | archive-date = 2011-04-16 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.pcgamer.com/2011/04/13/portal-2-levels-appear-in-potato-sack-games-clues-suggest-portal-2-could-be-released-early/ | title = Portal 2 levels appear in potato sack games, clues suggest Portal 2 could be released early | first = Tom | last = Senior | date = 2011-04-13 | accessdate = 2011-04-13 | work = [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110416053452/http://www.pcgamer.com/2011/04/13/portal-2-levels-appear-in-potato-sack-games-clues-suggest-portal-2-could-be-released-early | archive-date = 2011-04-16 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2011/04/valve-may-release-portal-2-on-friday-not-tuesday/ | title = Valve May Release Portal 2 On Friday, Not Tuesday | first = Chris | last = Kohler | date = 2011-04-13 | accessdate = 2011-04-13 | work = [[连线|Wired]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110416065828/http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2011/04/valve-may-release-portal-2-on-friday-not-tuesday | archive-date = 2011-04-16 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。4月15日，玩家们发现了“GLaDOS@Home”，一个伪装成[[分布式计算|分布式计算]]，鼓励大家参与以提前解锁《传送门2》的游戏<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamepro.com/article/news/218877/play-indie-games-help-portal-2-release-early/ | title = Play indie games, help Portal 2 release early | first = Pete | last = Davidson | date = 2011-04-15 | accessdate = 2011-04-15 | publisher = [[GamePro|GamePro]] | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/news/218877/play-indie-games-help-portal-2-release-early/&date=2011-11-30+19:02:35 | archivedate = 2011-11-30 | deadurl = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2011/04/portal-2-early-launch/ | title = Play Steam Games, Launch Portal 2 Early | first = Jason | last = Schreier | date = 2011-04-15 | accessdate = 2011-04-15 | work = [[连线|Wired]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110418184148/http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2011/04/portal-2-early-launch | archive-date = 2011-04-18 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。一旦谜题被解开，《传送门2》就可以提前十个小时解锁<ref name="vg247 early release">{{cite web | url = http://www.vg247.com/2011/04/19/portal-2-available-now/ | title = No more potatoes: Portal 2 available right now on Steam | first = Brenna | last = Hillier | date = 2011-04-18 | accessdate = 2011-04-18 | publisher = [[VG247|VG247]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110420083833/http://www.vg247.com/2011/04/19/portal-2-available-now/ | archive-date = 2011-04-20 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

维尔福制作了一系列《传送门2》的电视广告。维尔福曾与广告公司展开合作，但道格·隆巴尔迪发现广告公司的作品缺乏创意。他对抄袭、陈词滥调和表里不一的宣传感到不满<ref name="vg247 portal2 ad">{{cite web | url = http://www.vg247.com/2011/03/17/valves-in-house-portal-2-ads-the-result-of-copycat-agency-treatments/ | title = Valve's in-house Portal 2 ad the result of "copycat" agency treatments (Update) | first = Brenna | last = Hillier | date = 2011-03-17 | accessdate = 2011-03-17 | publisher = [[VG247|VG247]] | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/663Whb2Sw?url=http://www.vg247.com/2011/03/17/valves-in-house-portal-2-ads-the-result-of-copycat-agency-treatments/ | archive-date = 2012-03-10 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。根据观众的反馈情况，维尔福决定自己专门进行广告设计，直到大家满意为止。广告设计最终花了八个星期的时间<ref name="vg247 portal2 ad" />。维尔福还制作了以角色卡夫·强森的口吻来进行叙述的视频，以展示《传送门2》新加入的游戏元素。这些视频被加布·纽维尔称为是“纪录片式投资机会”的一部分<ref>{{cite news | url = http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gamehunters/post/2011/03/trailer-park-portal-2-1/1 | title = Trailer Park: 'Portal 2' | first = Brett | last = Molina | date = 2011-03-22 | accessdate = 2011-03-22 | work = [[今日美國|USA Today]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110326212019/http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gamehunters/post/2011/03/trailer-park-portal-2-1/1 | archive-date = 2011-03-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。维尔福在较早的时候发布了一个视频，对《传送门2》合作模式进行了宣传，并将其称为[[圣瓦伦丁|圣瓦伦丁]]的礼物。隆巴尔迪说这部视频“激发了我们的预售，打通了我们的电话，点亮了所有可以被出版商和发行商用于统计的指标”<ref name="fastcompany portal2" />。维尔福还推出了《传送门2》风格的商品，例如海报、水杯、T恤衫等<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamepro.com/article/news/218934/portal-2-goodies-now-on-sale/ | title = Portal 2 goodies now on sale | first = Pete | last = Davidson | date = 2011-04-19 | accessdate = 2011-04-19 | publisher = [[GamePro|GamePro]] | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/news/218934/portal-2-goodies-now-on-sale/&date=2011-11-30+19:03:07 | archivedate = 2011-11-30 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

=== 附加内容和可追加下载内容 ===
{{Imageframe|width=250|content=[[File:Valve_hammer_editor.jpg|250px]]<br />[[File:Portal_map_editor.jpg|250px]]|align=right|caption=玩家可通过[[Valve_Hammer_Editor|Valve Hammer Editor]]（上图）来制作《传送门2》的地图。后来维尔福发布了高度简化的地图编辑器，这样所有玩家都可以方便地制作自己的关卡。}}
《传送门2》包括一些附加内容，例如4个附加视频、《Lab Rat》漫画、電影《[[超級8|超級8]]》的交互式预告片等<ref>{{Cite news | url = http://www.pcgamer.com/2011/04/19/portal-2-has-hidden-interactive-super-8-teaser-level/ | title = Portal 2 has hidden interactive Super 8 teaser level | first = Tom | last = Senior | date = 2011-04-19 | accessdate = 2011-04-19 | work = [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110422112527/http://www.pcgamer.com/2011/04/19/portal-2-has-hidden-interactive-super-8-teaser-level/ | archive-date = 2011-04-22 | dead-url = no }}</ref>、“机器人自定义”（Robot Enrichment）功能。“机器人自定义”可以使玩家改变合作模式角色的手势和装饰物等。这些装饰可以在游戏中获得，也可以通过与其他玩家进行交易，或在游戏商店进行购买来获得<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.pcgamer.com/2011/04/19/portal-2-has-item-store-trading-coming-soon/ | title = Portal 2 has item store, trading coming soon | first = Tom | last = Senior | date = 2011-04-19 | accessdate = 2011-04-19 | work = [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110429013029/http://www.pcgamer.com/2011/04/19/portal-2-has-item-store-trading-coming-soon | archive-date = 2011-04-29 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

维尔福还计划给《传送门2》加入[[追加下载内容|追加下载内容]]。第一个DLC叫做“同儕評審”（{{lang-en|Peer Review}}），于2011年10月4日发布<ref name="fastcompany portal2">{{cite web | url = http://www.fastcompany.com/1750003/portal-2-valve-eric-wolpaw-jeep-barnett-doug-lombardi | title = Portal 2's Creators On Crafting Games Through Experiential Stories | first = Kevin | last = Ohannessian | date = 2011-04-27 | accessdate = 2011-04-27 | publisher = [[Fast_Company|Fast Company]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110430132704/http://www.fastcompany.com/1750003/portal-2-valve-eric-wolpaw-jeep-barnett-doug-lombardi | archive-date = 2011-04-30 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="eurog peer review">{{cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-09-30-portal-2-dlc-release-date | title = Portal 2 DLC release date | first = Fred | last = Dutton | date = 2011-09-30 | accessdate = 2011-09-30 | publisher = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111002143400/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-09-30-portal-2-dlc-release-date | archive-date = 2011-10-02 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-08-18-free-portal-2-dlc-out-next-month | title = Free Portal 2 DLC out next month | publisher = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | first = Fred | last = Dutton | date = 2011-08-18 | accessdate = 2011-08-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110828193924/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-08-18-free-portal-2-dlc-out-next-month | archive-date = 2011-08-28 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-10-04-portal-2-peer-review-dlc-is-1-37gb | title = Portal 2 Peer Review DLC is 1.37GB | first = Robert | last = Purchase | date = 2011-10-04 | accessdate = 2011-10-04 | publisher = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111005214559/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-10-04-portal-2-peer-review-dlc-is-1-37gb | archive-date = 2011-10-05 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。它是免费的，而且与玩家游戏平台无关。其中包含一个新的合作模式关卡。关卡剧情设定在合作模式剧情结束之后一星期，GLaDOS准备将两位机器人主角培养成“杀人机器”，以消灭在单人模式剧情中把土豆GLaDOS叼走的那只鸟<ref>{{cite web | url = http://arstechnica.com/gaming/reviews/2011/10/portal-2-peer-review-fun-but-missing-the-magic.ars | title = Portal 2 Peer Review DLC: fun, but missing the magic | first = Peter | last = Bright | date = 2011-10-09 | accessdate = 2011-10-11 | publisher = Ars Technica | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111009222148/http://arstechnica.com/gaming/reviews/2011/10/portal-2-peer-review-fun-but-missing-the-magic.ars | archive-date = 2011-10-09 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。DLC还加入了与前作类似的“挑战模式”，玩家需要尽量用最短时间或最少的传送门来解决谜题。玩家可以透過挑戰模式的記分板與好友們或整個《傳送門2》社群互相較勁分數。单人模式和合作模式都加入了挑战模式<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/34403/Valve_Offering_Free_Portal_2_DLC_On_All_Platforms_This_Summer.php | title = Valve Offering Free Portal 2 DLC On All Available Platforms This Summer | first = Kyle | last = Orland | date = 2011-04-29 | accessdate = 2011-04-29 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110501024250/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/34403/Valve_Offering_Free_Portal_2_DLC_On_All_Platforms_This_Summer.php | archive-date = 2011-05-01 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gamehunters/post/2011/04/free-dlc-for-portal-2-launching-this-summer/1 | title = Free DLC for 'Portal 2' launching this summer | work = [[今日美國|USA Today]] | date = 2011-04-29 | accessdate = 2011-04-29 | first = Brett | last = Molina | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110504023015/http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gamehunters/post/2011/04/free-dlc-for-portal-2-launching-this-summer/1 | archive-date = 2011-05-04 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

切特·费里斯诗克指出，玩家针对《传送门2》的[[用户生成内容|用户生成内容]]都可以在全部平台上运行，但是，由于软件依赖性的缘故，模组的制作软件只能在Windows系统上运行<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.nowgamer.com/news/919495/portal_2_mod_levels_for_all_platforms.html | title = Portal 2 Mod Levels 'For All Platforms' | publisher = NowGamer | date = 2001-01-24 | accessdate = 2011-06-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120120224936/http://www.nowgamer.com/news/919495/portal_2_mod_levels_for_all_platforms.html | archive-date = 2012-01-20 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。维尔福于2011年5月10日发布了模组制作软件的公开测试版本<ref>{{cite web | url = http://kotaku.com/5800623/now-you-can-make-your-own-portal-2-puzzles-i-said-now | title = Now You Can Make Your Own Custom ''Portal 2'' Puzzles (I Said NOW!!) | first = Michael | last = McWhertor | publisher = Kotaku | date = 2011-05-10 | accessdate = 2011-06-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110514142654/http://kotaku.com/5800623/now-you-can-make-your-own-portal-2-puzzles-i-said-now | archive-date = 2011-05-14 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2011年5月，维尔福支持了一场由-{zh-cn:社区;zh-tw:社群;}-举办的比赛，而且向最受欢迎的地图作者颁发了奖励<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.pcgamer.com/2011/05/26/portal-2-mapping-contest-kicks-off/ | title = Portal 2 mapping contest kicks off | first = Tom | last = Senior | date = 2011-05-26 | accessdate = 2011-10-11 | work = [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110807093335/http://www.pcgamer.com/2011/05/26/portal-2-mapping-contest-kicks-off/ | archive-date = 2011-08-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2012年5月8日，《传送门2》引入了“永久测试行动计划”（{{lang-en|Perpetual Testing Initiative}}），其中包括一个全新的地图编辑器，玩家可以-{zh-cn:通过; zh-tw:透過}-Steam的创意工坊下载和上传自定义地图<ref>{{cite web | url = http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gamehunters/post/2012/04/portal-2-puzzle-creator-launches-may-8/1#.T5mlLatYtSM | title = 'Portal 2' puzzle creator launches May 8 | work = [[今日美國|USA Today]] | date = 2012-04-26 | accessdate = 2012-04-26 | first = Brett | last = Molina | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120501183927/http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gamehunters/post/2012/04/portal-2-puzzle-creator-launches-may-8/1#.T5mlLatYtSM | archive-date = 2012-05-01 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.theverge.com/gaming/2012/4/26/2977445/portal-2-level-creation-steam | title = 'Portal 2' gets level creation tools May 8th for PC and Mac | first = Griffin | last = McElroy | date = 2012-04-26 | accessdate = 2012-04-26 | publisher = [[Polygon|Polygon]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120427190132/http://www.theverge.com/gaming/2012/4/26/2977445/portal-2-level-creation-steam | archive-date = 2012-04-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2011年11月，《{{le|GTTV|GameTrailers TV with Geoff Keighley}}》节目主持人{{le|杰夫·基思利|Geoff Keighley}}提到维尔福正在开发一个简化的地图编辑器，这样新手就可以在不接触[[Valve_Hammer_Editor|Valve Hammer Editor]]的前提下设计新实验室。此外，Valve还制作了一个可以-{zh-cn:通过; zh-tw:透過}-Steam创意工坊发布地图的系统<ref name="kotaku keighley editor">{{cite web | url = http://kotaku.com/5851007/valve-tinkering-with-an-excellent-portal-2-feature-that-talks-back | title = Valve Tinkering With an Excellent Portal 2 Feature That Talks Back | first = Stephan | last = Tolito | date = 2011-10-18 | accessdate = 2011-10-19 | publisher = Kotaku | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111020121041/http://kotaku.com/5851007/valve-tinkering-with-an-excellent-portal-2-feature-that-talks-back | archive-date = 2011-10-20 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="pcgamer editor beta"/>。这个系统于2012年3月投入公开测试<ref name="pcgamer editor beta">{{cite web | url = http://www.pcgamer.com/2012/03/14/portal-2-puzzle-creator-in-beta-testing-now-will-use-steam-workshop/ | title = Portal 2 Puzzle Creator in internal beta testing now, will use Steam Workshop | first = Tom | last = Senior | date = 2012-03-14 | accessdate = 2012-03-14 | work = [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120316182343/http://www.pcgamer.com/2012/03/14/portal-2-puzzle-creator-in-beta-testing-now-will-use-steam-workshop/ | archive-date = 2012-03-16 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/38044/Portal_2_Sees_Map_Editor_Next_Year.php | title = Portal 2 Sees Map Editor Next Year | first = Frank | last = Cifaldi | date = 2011-10-21 | accessdate = 2011-10-21 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111023191550/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/38044/Portal_2_Sees_Map_Editor_Next_Year.php | archive-date = 2011-10-23 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在“永久测试行动计划”发布之后，几天之内就产生了35,000张地图，这些地图在Steam上面总共被下载了1300万次<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2012/05/10/portal-2-39-s-perpetual-testing-initiative-off-to-a-good-start.aspx | title = Portal 2's Perpetual Testing Initiative Off To A Good Start | first = Matt | last = Helgeson | date = 2012-05-10 | accessdate = 2012-05-11 | work = [[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120512040310/http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2012/05/10/portal-2-39-s-perpetual-testing-initiative-off-to-a-good-start.aspx | archive-date = 2012-05-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。一个月之内，地图数量超过了150,000<ref name="gamasutra teachwithportals"/>。“永久测试行动计划”最初只支持单人模式地图。2012年8月16日，维尔福发布了一个补丁，使得玩家可以制作合作模式的地图<ref>{{cite web |url=http://pc.gamespy.com/articles/122/1225780p1.html |title=Valve Announces Documentary Film on Pro Gaming, Portal 2 Co-Op Map Maker |first=Mike |last=Sharkley |date=2012-08-17 |accessdate=2012-08-17 |publisher=[[GameSpy|GameSpy]] |archivedate=2013-02-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130203125658/http://pc.gamespy.com/articles/122/1225780p1.html |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

截至2013年1月，维尔福一直在支持爱好者们利用《传送门2》的内容进行再创作，并且还提供协助和部分素材。游戏《[[堡垒_(2011年游戏)|堡垒]]》中有一款武器受到了《传送门2》中转换凝胶和炮塔的启发，而且游戏的开发者[[Supergiant_Games|Supergiant Games]]公司在剧本方面得到了艾瑞克·沃保的协助，游戏中炮塔的配音是由愛倫·麥克萊恩完成的<ref>{{cite web | url = http://arstechnica.com/gaming/news/2011/08/bastion-on-the-pc-now-youre-thinking-with-portals.ars | title = Bastion on PC? Now you're thinking with portals | date = 2011-08-22 | accessdate = 2011-08-23 | publisher = Ars Technica | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6ADncbZdd?url=http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2011/08/bastion-on-the-pc-now-youre-thinking-with-portals/ | archive-date = 2012-08-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。{{tsl|en|Hidden Path Entertainment|Hidden Path Entertainment}}公司的[[塔防游戏|塔防游戏]]《{{tsl|en|Defense Grid: The Awakening|防御阵型：觉醒}}》加入了GLaDOS角色，并使用了愛倫·麥克萊恩新录制的对话和《传送门2》的素材<ref>{{Cite press release | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/pressreleases/80521/Portalrsquos_GLaDOS_Invades_the_World_of_DefenseGrid.php | title = Portal’s GLaDOS Invades the World of Defense Grid! | publisher = {{tsl|en|Hidden Path Entertainment||Hidden Path Entertainment}} | accessdate = 2011-12-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120113082616/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/pressreleases/80521/Portalrsquos_GLaDOS_Invades_the_World_of_DefenseGrid.php | archive-date = 2012-01-13 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。沃保和麥克萊恩还帮助过一个名为加里·哈得森（Gary Hudston）的地图作者，为他设计了额外的剧情对话，而这个地图将被作者用于向自己的未婚妻求婚<ref>{{cite news | url = http://techland.time.com/2011/08/23/custom-portal-2-video-game-level-built-for-marriage-proposal/ | title = Custom 'Portal 2' Video Game Level Built for Marriage Proposal | first = Evan | last = Narcisse | date = 2011-08-23 | accessdate = 2011-08-23 | work = [[時代_(雜誌)|Time]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110919074825/http://techland.time.com/2011/08/23/custom-portal-2-video-game-level-built-for-marriage-proposal/ | archive-date = 2011-09-19 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/36788/Behind_The_Scenes_Of_The_Portal_Proposal.php | title = Behind The Scenes Of The Portal Proposal | first = Chris | last = Morris | date = 2011-08-26 | accessdate = 2011-08-26 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110925024514/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/36788/Behind_The_Scenes_Of_The_Portal_Proposal.php | archive-date = 2011-09-25 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[贝塞斯达软件公司|贝塞斯达公司]]为《[[上古卷轴V：天际|上古卷轴V：天际]]》发布了一个补丁，加入了对[[Steam|Steam]]创意工坊的支持，于是维尔福为上古卷轴制作了一个免费的[[遊戲模組|遊戲模組]]，将太空核心作为一个角色纳入了游戏之中<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.shacknews.com/article/72350/skyrim-hd-textures-portal-2-dlc | title = Skyrim gets HD texture pack, Portal 2 Space Sphere | publisher = [[Shacknews|Shacknews]] | date = 2012-02-07 | accessdate = 2012-02-07 | first = Alice | last = O'Conner | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120208225406/http://www.shacknews.com/article/72350/skyrim-hd-textures-portal-2-dlc | archive-date = 2012-02-08 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。维尔福与{{tsl|en|Zen Studios|Zen Studios}}工作室进行合作，共同为《{{tsl|en|Pinball FX 2|三维弹球FX2}}》和《{{tsl|en|Zen Pinball|Zen Pinball}}》做出了具有《传送门2》风格和其他维尔福风格的弹球球台<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.pcgamer.com/portal-pinball-hands-on-with-pinball-fx2s-new-portal-themed-table/ | title = Portal Pinball: hands-on with Pinball FX2's new Portal themed table | first = Tom | last = Marks | date = 2015-05-05 | accessdate = 2015-05-05 | work = [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150508020103/http://www.pcgamer.com/portal-pinball-hands-on-with-pinball-fx2s-new-portal-themed-table/ | archive-date = 2015-05-08 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在[[华纳兄弟|华纳兄弟]]制作的《{{tsl|en|Lego Dimensions|乐高：次元}}》中也能找到传送门风格的套件。这部游戏还加入了一些额外的剧情，由华纳兄弟的Traveller's Tales工作室和维尔福共同编写，剧情设定在《传送门2》剧情结束之后。愛倫·麥克萊恩、斯蒂芬·默切特和J·K·西蒙斯仍然为原来的角色配音，乔纳森·库尔顿仍然创作主题曲，而主题曲还是由愛倫·麥克萊恩来演唱<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.polygon.com/2015/5/10/8583417/lego-dimensions-leak-portal-dr-who-jurassic-world-the-simpsons | title = Portal, Dr. Who, The Simpsons and more confirmed for Lego Dimensions | publisher = [[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]] | first = Michael | last = McWhertor | date = 2015-05-10 | accessdate = 2015-05-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150512160424/http://www.polygon.com/2015/5/10/8583417/lego-dimensions-leak-portal-dr-who-jurassic-world-the-simpsons | archive-date = 2015-05-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

