=== PlayStation 3 ===
《传送门2》支持[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]的决定惊动了电子游戏界，因为加布·纽维尔之前批评过PlayStation，还指出把《[[橙盒|橙盒]]》移植到PlayStation上面很困难<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.pcworld.com/article/198935/valve_apologizes_for_sonybashing_announces_portal_2_for_ps3.html?tk=hp_blg | title = Valve Apologizes For Sony-Bashing, Announces Portal 2 for PS3 | first = Matt | last = Peckham | date = 2010-06-15 | accessdate = 2010-06-15 | work = [[PC_World_(magazine)|PC World]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100619071727/http://www.pcworld.com/article/198935/valve_apologizes_for_sonybashing_announces_portal_2_for_ps3.html?tk=hp_blg | archive-date = 2010-06-19 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。维尔福对微软关于[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]的政策越来越失望，例如向玩家推送[[修補程式|修補程式]]和新内容很困难，这导致维尔福转向了PlayStation 3。纽维尔发现索尼的发布模型更为开放，允许开发者加入跟[[Steam|Steam]]类似的功能<ref name="final hours"/>。《传送门2》是第一款支持部分[[Steam|Steamworks]]组件功能的PlayStation 3游戏，其中包括自动更新、追加下载内容和-{zh-cn:社区;zh-tw:社群;}-支持等<ref>{{cite web | url = http://e3.gamespot.com/story/6265808/portal-2-steamworks-ps3-bound-in-2011 | title = Portal 2, Steamworks PS3-bound in 2011 | publisher = [[GameSpot|Gamespot]] | first = Tor | last = Thorsen | date = 2010-06-15 | accessdate = 2010-06-16 | archivedate = 2012-03-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120313222355/http://e3.gamespot.com/story/6265808/portal-2-steamworks-ps3-bound-in-2011 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。游戏还具有跨平台支持，即与使用不同设备和操作系统的玩家共同游戏<ref name="ps3 crossplatform">{{cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-01-18-portal-2-ps3-steam-cross-platform-play | title = Portal 2 PS3, Steam cross-platform play | first = Wesley | last = Yin-Poole | date = 2011-01-18 | accessdate = 2010-01-18 | publisher = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303221700/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-01-18-portal-2-ps3-steam-cross-platform-play | archive-date = 2016-03-03 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

游戏的Steam层可以同时显示来自Steam和[[PlayStation_Network|PlayStation Network]]的好友，并且可以同时显示来自Steam和PlayStation Network的[[成就_(电子游戏)|成就]]<ref name="cvg p2 steamworks">{{cite web | url =http://www.computerandvideogames.com/298024/news/valve-details-ps3-steam-support-for-portal-2/ | title =Valve details PS3 Steam support for Portal 2 | work =[[电脑与电子游戏|Computer and Video Games]] | date =2011-04-13 | accessdate =2011-04-13 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20110416054453/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/298024/news/valve-details-ps3-steam-support-for-portal-2/ | archive-date =2011-04-16 | dead-url =no }}</ref>。PlayStation 3玩家可以在不支付额外费用的情况下获取电脑版本<ref name="ps3 crossplatform" /><ref name="cvg p2 steamworks" />。集成Steamworks功能使得维尔福能够收集发布之后玩家遇到的问题，然后发布合适的更新<ref name="telegraph interview" />。维尔福曾宣布他们不打算在游戏中集成其他PlayStation 3的功能，例如[[3D立體電視|3D立體電視]]或[[PlayStation_Move|PlayStation Move]]等<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.computerandvideogames.com/253007/valve-no-plans-for-3d-move-support-in-portal-2/ | title = Valve 'no plans' for 3D, Move support in Portal 2 | publisher = [[电脑与电子游戏|Computer and Video Games]] | date = 2010-06-22 | accessdate = 2010-06-22 | first = Tim | last = Ingham | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120105185436/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/253007/valve-no-plans-for-3d-move-support-in-portal-2/ | archive-date = 2012-01-05 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.shacknews.com/article/67555/portal-2-on-ps3-will | title = Portal 2 on PS3 Will Not Feature Move Support (Updated) | first = Steve | last = Watts | date = 2011-02-17 | accessdate = 2011-02-17 | publisher = [[Shacknews|Shacknews]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110404113831/http://www.shacknews.com/article/67555/portal-2-on-ps3-will | archive-date = 2011-04-04 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。然而维尔福在2012年6月宣布将于年底发布针对PlayStation 3版本的补丁，以支持[[PlayStation_Move|PlayStation Move]]控制器，而且会以“Portal 2 In Motion”的名字加入一些额外内容，这些内容也曾经提供给九头灵蛇控制器版本<ref>{{cite web | url = http://kotaku.com/5915992/portal-picks-up-a-playstation-move-controller-returns-to-the-ps3-with-new-levels | title = Portal Picks Up a PlayStation Move Controller, Returns to the PS3 With New Levels | first = Luke | last = Plunkett | date = 2012-06-05 | accessdate = 2012-06-05 | publisher = Kotaku | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120608033319/http://kotaku.com/5915992/portal-picks-up-a-playstation-move-controller-returns-to-the-ps3-with-new-levels | archive-date = 2012-06-08 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。补丁于2012年11月发布<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.computerandvideogames.com/377130/portal-2-in-motion-dlc-out-in-us-today-launch-trailer/ | title = Portal 2 'In Motion' DLC out in US today, launch trailer | publisher = [[电脑与电子游戏|Computer & Video Games]] | date = 2012-11-06 | accessdate = 2012-11-06 | first = Mike | last = Jackson | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121109085616/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/377130/portal-2-in-motion-dlc-out-in-us-today-launch-trailer/ | archive-date = 2012-11-09 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2013年6月维尔福又向“Portal 2 In Motion”加入了一个免费的合作模式扩展<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-06-06-portal-2s-ps3-dlc-in-motion-gets-a-free-co-op-campaign | title = Portal 2's Move-based In Motion DLC gets a free co-op campaign | publisher = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | date = 2013-06-06 | accessdate = 2013-06-06 | first = Jeffrey | last = Matulef | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130609044914/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-06-06-portal-2s-ps3-dlc-in-motion-gets-a-free-co-op-campaign | archive-date = 2013-06-09 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。维尔福表示，尽管为PlayStation 3提供了超过Xbox 360的额外支持，但是游戏的核心部分在各平台都是一样的<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.vg247.com/2011/01/22/the-core-portal-2-game-is-the-same-whether-you-buy-it-on-ps3-or-360-says-valve/ | title = Core Portal 2 game is the same "whether you buy it on PS3 or 360", says Valve | date = 2011-01-22 | accessdate = 2011-01-24 | first = Stephany | last = Nunneley | publisher = [[VG247|VG247]] | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/663WevSJl?url=http://www.vg247.com/2011/01/22/the-core-portal-2-game-is-the-same-whether-you-buy-it-on-ps3-or-360-says-valve/ | archive-date = 2012-03-10 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

