《传送门2》在发售后受到了普遍好评，在评分综合网站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得到了95分的高分<ref>{{cite web | url = http://gamasutra.com/view/news/34200/Critical_Reception_Valves_Portal_2.php | title = Critical Reception: Valve's Portal 2 | first = Danny | last = Cowen | date = 2011-04-20 | accessdate = 2011-04-20 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110423030610/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/34200/Critical_Reception_Valves_Portal_2.php | archive-date = 2011-04-23 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，而且在整个2011年于不同平台获得了第三至第五的排名<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.computerandvideogames.com/332121/batman-arkham-city-ps3-is-metacritics-game-of-the-year/ | title = Narrowly beats The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim on Xbox 360 to take the top review spot | work = [[电脑与电子游戏|Computer and Video Games]] | date = 2012-01-13 | accessdate = 2012-01-13 | first = Tom | last = Ivan | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120115230858/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/332121/batman-arkham-city-ps3-is-metacritics-game-of-the-year/ | archive-date = 2012-01-15 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。一些评论者认为《传送门2》是“年度游戏”的有力竞争者<ref name="1up review">{{cite web | url = http://www.1up.com/reviews/portal-2-review | title = Portal 2 Review | accessdate = 2011-04-21 | publisher = [[1UP.com|1UP.com]] | first = Mike | last = Nelson | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/663WzgJB7?url=http://www.1up.com/reviews/portal-2-review | archivedate = 2012-03-10 }}</ref><ref name="eurogamer review">{{cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-04-19-portal-2-review | title = Portal 2 | first = Oli | last = Welsh | date = 2011-04-19 | accessdate = 2011-04-19 | publisher = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/663XBDF41?url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-04-19-portal-2-review | archive-date = 2012-03-10 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="usatoday review">{{cite news | url = http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gamehunters/post/2011/04/review-portal-2-aces-the-sequel-test/1 | title = Review: 'Portal 2' aces the sequel test | first = Brett | last = Molina | date = 2011-04-19 | accessdate = 2011-04-19 | work = [[今日美國|USA Today]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110420221905/http://content.usatoday.com/communities/gamehunters/post/2011/04/review-portal-2-aces-the-sequel-test/1 | archive-date = 2011-04-20 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="globeandmail review">{{cite news | url = http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/technology/video-games/game-reviews/review-portal-2-is-for-smarty-pants-only/article2004276/ | title = Portal 2 is for smarty-pants only | first = Chad | last = Sapieha | work = [[环球邮报|Globe and Mail]] | date = 2011-05-01 | accessdate = 2011-05-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110503194033/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/technology/video-games/game-reviews/review-portal-2-is-for-smarty-pants-only/article2004276/ | archive-date = 2011-05-03 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，而其他人则将其称为{{tsl|en|List of video games considered the best|被评为最好的电子游戏列表|有史以来最棒的游戏之一}}<ref name="telegraph review"/><ref name="g4 review">{{cite web | url = http://www.g4tv.com/games/xbox-360/63787/portal-2/review/ | title = Portal 2 Review – Xbox 360 | first = Morgan | last = Webb | date = 2011-04-19 | accessdate = 2011-04-19 | publisher = [[G4_(电视频道)|G4 (电视频道)]] | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/663XFBP8u?url=http://www.g4tv.com/games/xbox-360/63787/portal-2/review/ | archive-date = 2012-03-10 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref name="guardian review">{{cite news | url = http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/gamesblog/2011/apr/19/portal-2-game-review | title = Portal 2 – Review | date = 2011-04-19 | accessdate = 2011-04-19 | work = [[衛報|The Guardian]] | first = Nick | last = Cowen | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110423045227/http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/gamesblog/2011/apr/19/portal-2-game-review | archive-date = 2011-04-23 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="observer review">{{cite news | url = http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/2011/apr/24/portal-2-will-freeman-review | title = Portal 2 – review | first = Will | last = Freeman | date = 2011-04-23 | accessdate = 2011-04-23 | work = [[觀察家報|The Observer]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110426070821/http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/2011/apr/24/portal-2-will-freeman-review | archive-date = 2011-04-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="wsj review">{{cite news | url = http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2011/04/19/portal-2-is-a-hole-in-one/ | title = Portal 2 Is A Hole In One | first = Ryan | last = Kuo | date = 2011-04-19 | accessdate = 2011-04-19 | work = [[华尔街日报|Wall Street Journal]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110425041138/http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2011/04/19/portal-2-is-a-hole-in-one/ | archive-date = 2011-04-25 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。人们普遍认为《传送门2》跟前作一样好，甚至更好。[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]的奥利·威尔士（Oli Welsh）说游戏避开了开发商在开发续集时的缺陷，指出“《传送门》是很完美的，但《传送门2》不是。《传送门2》比完美更完美。”<ref name="eurogamer review" />[[影音俱樂部|影音俱樂部]]的古斯·马斯特拉帕（Gus Mastrapa）写道，维尔福消除了先前人们对《传送门》的猜疑——其实《传送门》的剧情也可以扩展得更为翔实<ref name="avclub review">{{cite web | url = http://www.avclub.com/articles/portal-2,55020/ | title = Portal 2 | first = Gus | last = Mastrapa | date = 2011-04-25 | accessdate = 2011-04-25 | publisher = [[影音俱樂部|A.V. Club]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110429164739/http://www.avclub.com/articles/portal-2%2C55020/ | archive-date = 2011-04-29 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[IGN|IGN]]的查尔斯·奥日特（Charles Onyett）写道，续集通过拓展游戏的玩法和剧情“使前作看起来更像是原型”<ref name="ign review">{{cite web | url = http://uk.pc.ign.com/articles/116/1162215p1.html | title = Portal 2 Review | first = Charles | last = Onyett | date = 2011-04-19 | accessdate = 2011-04-19 | publisher = IGN | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/663X6ENdj?url=http://uk.pc.ign.com/articles/116/1162215p1.html | archive-date = 2012-03-10 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

大多数评论者赞扬了游戏的创作和配音<ref name="1up review" /><ref name="bostonherald review">{{cite news | url = http://www.bostonherald.com/entertainment/music/reviews/view.bg?articleid=1333006 | title = ‘Portal 2’ sure to gel with fans | first = Garrett | last = Martin | date = 2011-04-25 | accessdate = 2011-05-01 | work = {{tsl|en|Boston Herald||Boston Herald}} | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121005103110/http://www.bostonherald.com/entertainment/music/reviews/view.bg?articleid=1333006 | archive-date = 2012-10-05 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="cnn review">{{cite news | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2011/TECH/gaming.gadgets/04/19/portal.2.review/ | title = 'Portal 2' is a dark, humorous joy (and that's no lie) | first = Larry | last = Frum | date = 2011-04-19 | accessdate = 2011-04-19 | publisher = CNN | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120114154516/http://edition.cnn.com/2011/TECH/gaming.gadgets/04/19/portal.2.review/ | archive-date = 2012-01-14 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="time review">{{cite news | url = http://techland.time.com/2011/04/19/portal-2-review-our-first-perfect-10/print/ | title = Portal 2 Review: Our First Perfect 10 | first = Evan | last = Narcisse | date = 2011-04-19 | accessdate = 2011-04-19 | work = [[時代_(雜誌)|Time]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131110204135/http://techland.time.com/2011/04/19/portal-2-review-our-first-perfect-10/print/ | archive-date = 2013-11-10 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》和《[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]》杂志的丹·斯特普尔顿（Dan Stapleton）能够预测游戏剧情中的许多曲折，但“仍然期待看到游戏角色的反应”。他对游戏角色的设计持正面评价，正如“他们的魅力使得原本将要回归虚无的世界变得喧闹和富有生机”<ref name="pc gamer us review">{{cite web | url = http://www.pcgamer.com/2011/04/19/portal-2-review/ | title = Portal 2 review | first = Dan | last = Stapleton | date = 2011-04-19 | accessdate = 2011-04-26 | work = [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] | archivedate = 2015-12-31 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151231054205/http://www.pcgamer.com/portal-2-review/?ssoGetComments=%221451540553949%22&flexicache=disabled | dead-url = no }}</ref>。各角色都受到了好评<ref name="edge review">{{cite web |url=http://www.next-gen.biz/reviews/portal-2-review |title=Portal 2 Review |date=2011-04-19 |accessdate=2011-04-30 |work=[[Edge_(杂志)|Edge]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110829011356/http://www.next-gen.biz/reviews/portal-2-review |archivedate=2011-08-29 }}</ref><ref name="g4 review" /><ref name="globeandmail review"/><ref name="ew review">{{cite web | url = http://popwatch.ew.com/2011/04/20/portal-2-review/ | title = 'Portal 2' videogame review: Physics is phunny | first = John | last = Young | date = 2011-04-20 | accessdate = 2011-04-20 | work = [[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110420141435/http://popwatch.ew.com/2011/04/20/portal-2-review/ | archive-date = 2011-04-20 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。查尔斯·奥日特指出默切特“对角色有着明显的热情，这对游戏大有裨益”，并且“一贯聪明的写作与屏幕上的行动完美互补”<ref name="ign review" />。《[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]》月刊的亚当·比赛纳（Adam Biessener）认为卡夫·强森这个角色比GLaDOS还要出色，并赞扬了游戏的“完美音调传递”和“精彩的喜剧时间”<ref name="gi review">{{cite web | url = http://www.gameinformer.com/games/portal_2/b/pc/archive/2011/04/18/the-sequel-you-were-hoping-for.aspx | title = Portal 2 | first = Adam | last = Biessener | date = 2011-04-18 | accessdate = 2011-04-19 | work = [[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/663XENcZ3?url=http://www.gameinformer.com/games/portal_2/b/pc/archive/2011/04/18/the-sequel-you-were-hoping-for.aspx | archive-date = 2012-03-10 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。相反的是，[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]的彼得·布莱特（Peter Bright）认为，与他在玩《传送门》时感觉到的孤独和绝望相比，《传送门2》的惠特利和GLaDOS失去了一些这样的感觉，“只是扰乱了心情而已”<ref name="arstech review">{{cite web | url = http://arstechnica.com/gaming/reviews/2011/05/portal-2-a-good-game-but-not-a-great-one.ars/ | title = Thinking on rails: why Portal 2 isn't as good as the original | first = Peter | last = Bright | date = 2011-05-02 | accessdate = 2011-05-02 | publisher = Ars Technica | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110504230014/http://arstechnica.com/gaming/reviews/2011/05/portal-2-a-good-game-but-not-a-great-one.ars | archive-date = 2011-05-04 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

《传送门2》新引入的游戏元素，例如强光桥、高热能激光和凝胶等也受到了好评。评论者对游戏的难度感到满意，认为虽然第一眼看上去很复杂，但是实际上谜题的解法并不复杂<ref name="telegraph review"/><ref name="nytimes review">{{cite news | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2011/05/11/arts/video-games/portal-2-a-video-brain-game-review.html | title = Physics, With Wormholes by You | date = 2011-05-10 | accessdate = 2011-05-10 | first = Seth | last = Schiesel | work = [[纽约时报|New York Times]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110513085120/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/05/11/arts/video-games/portal-2-a-video-brain-game-review.html | archive-date = 2011-05-13 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="famitsu review 1up">{{cite web |url=http://www.1up.com/news/japan-review-check-portal-2 |title=Japan Review Check: Portal 2, Ghost Recon |first=Kevin |last=Gifford |date=2011-05-11 |accessdate=2011-05-11 |publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140106034438/http://www.1up.com/news/japan-review-check-portal-2 |archivedate=2014-01-06 }}</ref><ref name="gamespot review">{{cite web | url = http://www.gamespot.com/pc/action/portal-2/review.html | title = Portal 2 Review | first = Chris | last = Watters | date = 2011-04-19 | work = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | archivedate = 2011-10-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111029154135/http://www.gamespot.com/pc/action/portal-2/review.html | accessdate = 2015-09-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="globeandmail review"/><ref name="observer review"/><ref name="paste review">{{cite web | url = http://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2011/04/portal-2-review-multi.html | title = Portal 2 Review (Multi-Platform) | first = Kirk | last = Hamilton | date = 2011-04-26 | accessdate = 2011-05-05 | work = {{tsl|en|Paste (magazine)||Paste}} | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110429020210/http://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2011/04/portal-2-review-multi.html | archive-date = 2011-04-29 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。《时代》杂志的埃文·纳西斯（Evan Narcisse）担心新引入的元素会“淡化纯粹的体验，不过，维尔福有着高水平的魅力和气质，一切仍然很精巧”<ref name="time review"/>。《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》的汤姆·霍金斯（Tom Hoggins）赞扬游戏以一种“杰出的学习曲线而非简单的介绍”的形式来引入新元素，并认为这是一种“特别大方但处理方式奇特的设计精神”<ref name="telegraph review"/>。《[[连线|连线]]》杂志的克里斯·科勒（Chris Kohler）评论道“游戏从来不需要特别复杂的解法”，解决大多数谜题时都会遇到这样的场景：“拍打自己脑门，然后自己就在想，天啊，我真是个傻瓜！之前我怎么没想到呢？”<ref name="wired review">{{cite web | url = http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2011/04/portal-2-review/ | title = Portal 2 Review | date = 2011-04-21 | accessdate = 2011-04-21 | first = Jeff | last = Kohler | work = [[连线|Wired]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110424072543/http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2011/04/portal-2-review | archive-date = 2011-04-24 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。彼得·布莱特感觉《传送门2》要比前作简单，他发现游戏有效地向玩家进行了新元素的教学，并要求玩家“小心地使用已经提供的道具”，这给他的印象就是“游戏像在轨道上运行”<ref name="arstech review"/>。但是丹·斯特普尔顿对凝胶持负面评价，认为它“难以控制”，而且“最多也只有一点用途”<ref name="pc gamer us review"/>。

有评论强调合作模式关卡是游戏的一个有价值的补充<ref name="edge review"/><ref name="g4 review"/><ref name="gi review"/>。奥利·威尔士把合作模式称为“一个你可以与朋友共同进行的、最令人满意的、属于真正协作的游戏体验”<ref name="eurogamer review"/>。查尔斯·奥日特写道，“维尔福清楚一个好的合作模式应当如何进行设计。这不能是简单的鼓励，而是得要求你们一起工作。在《传送门2》中，沟通对成功至关重要。”<ref name="ign review"/>一些评论者对玩家之间可以-{zh-cn:通过; zh-tw:透過}-非语音方式进行沟通的设计表示称赞<ref name="gi review"/><ref name="gamespot review"/><ref name="ign review"/><ref name="usatoday review"/>。《传送门2》在设计、声音和音乐方面的细节都受到了赞誉<ref name="pc gamer us review"/>。迈克·纳尔逊（Mike Nelson）相信游戏的世界中置入了“绝对的细节”，“这一切感觉非常真实和自然，在一个短暂的时刻中觉得自己被引入了这个世界。”<ref name="1up review"/>查尔斯·奥日特对维尔福的[[起源引擎|起源引擎]]所能达到的丰富的细节和功能印象深刻，为关卡增加细节和动画“这一系列服务不光愉悦了我们的眼睛，而且还加深了我们对游戏角色的理解”<ref name="ign review"/>。汤姆·霍金斯评论道，游戏世界“以一种惊人和有机结合的方式”来对游戏主角雪儿作出反应，并称赞维尔福的设计“跟《[[生化奇兵|生化奇兵]]》的水下城市{{tsl|en|Rapture (BioShock)|销魂城}}一样达到了世界级的成就。”<ref name="telegraph review"/>

《传送门2》也有收到一些批评的声音。一些评论者认为游戏的第二幕{{efn|即单人模式中主角被惠特利抛入深渊，然后来到已被光圈科学废弃的陈旧设施那部分。}}可能会使一些玩家感到困惑。约翰·杨（John Young）写道，在第二幕，游戏“以一种会使比较随便的玩家沮丧的方式提高了难度”，特别是在离开一个实验室前往下一个实验室时，“我都不知道接下来应该去哪儿”<ref name="ew review"/>。克里斯·科勒写道，当玩家在光圈科技废弃设施中浏览时，“这些设施没有做任何事情——它只是一堆贫瘠、重复、非交互式的环境”<ref name="wired review"/>。克里斯·沃特斯（Chris Watters）说，与维尔福早期的游戏相反，《传送门2》各关卡之间的加载时间“太长以至于让你希望它短些”<ref name="gamespot review"/>。沃特斯还说，不幸的是，游戏缺乏“独立的实验室和排行榜……不过，即便没有这些东西，《传送门2》在内容方面也不肤浅”<ref name="gamespot review"/>。奥利·威尔士指出，如果想要在《传送门2》结束时重温前作主题曲《[[仍然活著|Still Alive]]》的感觉，那么这个决定是错误的<ref name="eurogamer review" />。游戏批评家{{tsl|en|Ben "Yahtzee" Croshaw|本·"雅兹"·克罗肖}}在他的“[[零标点符号|零标点符号]]”节目中称《传送门2》是2011年最佳游戏。然而，他认为虽然《传送门2》是一款非常优秀的游戏，但是它不必要地衔接了前作的部分故事，并没有真正进一步发展游戏的概念。不过这个批评只针对单人模式的剧情。对于合作模式，他指出这个模式有“更多的吸引力和更多的原创精神”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/articles/view/columns/extra-punctuation/8857-Building-Sequels-Badly |title=The Escapist : Building Sequels Badly |publisher=Escapistmagazine.com |date= |accessdate=2013-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130516042241/http://www.escapistmagazine.com/articles/view/columns/extra-punctuation/8857-Building-Sequels-Badly |archive-date=2013-05-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2011年4月20日，有报导指出玩家发起了一场针对《传送门2》缺陷的抗议活动<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2011-04-20-fans-protest-portal-2-on-metacritic|title=Fans protest Portal 2 on Metacritic|first=David|last=Jenkins|date=2011-04-20|accessdate=2011-04-20|publisher=GamesIndustry.biz|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110423192036/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2011-04-20-fans-protest-portal-2-on-metacritic|archive-date=2011-04-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.metro.co.uk/tech/games/861383-portal-2-hit-by-user-review-backlash-on-metacritic | title = Portal 2 hit by user review backlash on Metacritic | date = 2011-04-20 | accessdate = 2011-04-20 | work = {{tsl|en|Metro (British newspaper)||Metro}} | author = metrowebukmetro | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110424105413/http://www.metro.co.uk/tech/games/861383-portal-2-hit-by-user-review-backlash-on-metacritic | archive-date = 2011-04-24 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。玩家抱怨游戏长度太短——一些人说游戏全长只有四个小时，而且追加下载内容不值那么多的钱，而且有人说游戏画面没有特色，其电脑版只是游戏机版的简单移植。Kotaku的史蒂芬·托蒂罗（Stephen Totilo）指出，游戏全长达九个小时，追加下载内容纯粹是一些装饰性的附件<ref>{{cite web |url=http://kotaku.com/5793543/the-people-are-panning-portal-2 |title=The People are Panning Portal2 |date=2011-04-19 |last=Tolito |accessdate=2011-04-19 |publisher=Kotaku |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927182932/http://kotaku.com/5793543/the-people-are-panning-portal-2 |archive-date=2011-09-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。一些记者认为在《传送门2》之前发布的《马铃薯袋》可能对玩家评分造成了影响<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2011/04/19/lets-address-some-portal-2-nonsense/ |title=Let's Address Some Portal 2 Nonsense |first=John |last=Walker |date=2011-04-19 |accessdate=2011-04-19 |publisher=[[Rock,_Paper,_Shotgun|Rock Paper Shotgun]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110421034518/http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2011/04/19/lets-address-some-portal-2-nonsense/ |archive-date=2011-04-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-04-19-portal-2-metacritic-user-score-pounded|title=Portal 2 Metacritic user score pounded|publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|date=2011-04-19|accessdate=2011-04-19|first=Fred|last=Dutton|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110425034355/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-04-19-portal-2-metacritic-user-score-pounded|archive-date=2011-04-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

