玩游戏大奖|Spike电玩游戏大奖]]中获得了12项提名，包括“年度游戏”等<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/38603/Portal_2_Leads_Spike_TV_VGA_Nominees_With_12_Nods.php | title = Portal 2 Leads Spike TV VGA Nominees With 12 Nods | first = Kyle | last = Orland | date = 2011-11-16 | accessdate = 2011-11-16 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20111119014716/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/38603/Portal_2_Leads_Spike_TV_VGA_Nominees_With_12_Nods.php | archive-date = 2011-11-19 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，并赢得了“最佳PC游戏”、“最佳男演员”（授予斯蒂芬·默切特）和“最佳女演员”（授予愛倫·麥克萊恩）、“最佳DLC”和“最佳多人游戏”几个奖项<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2011/12/11/skyrim-portal-2-arkham-city-won-big-at-vgas.aspx | title = Skyrim, Portal 2, Arkham City Won Big At VGAs | first = Jeff | last = Cork | date = 2011-12-11 | accessdate = 2011-12-11 | work = [[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120106132343/http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2011/12/11/skyrim-portal-2-arkham-city-won-big-at-vgas.aspx | archive-date = 2012-01-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在2011年[[游戏开发者选择奖|游戏开发者选择奖]]中，《传送门2》赢得五项提名，包括“年度游戏”等<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/39507/Portal_2_Skyrim_Bastion_lead_finalists_for_12th_annual_Game_Developers_Choice_Awards.php | title = Portal 2, Skyrim, Bastion lead finalists for 12th annual Game Developers Choice Awards | date = 2012-01-05 | accessdate = 2012-01-05 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120108071505/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/39507/Portal_2_Skyrim_Bastion_lead_finalists_for_12th_annual_Game_Developers_Choice_Awards.php | archive-date = 2012-01-08 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，而且获得了“最佳叙事”、“最佳音效”和“最佳游戏设计”奖项<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/164945/Skyrim_wins_Game_of_the_Year_at_GDC_Awards.php | title = Skyrim wins Game of the Year at GDC Awards | date = 2012-03-08 | accessdate = 2012-03-08 | publi