rl = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-17410374 | title = Portal 2 wins best game at the Bafta Video Game Awards | date = 2012-03-16 | accessdate = 2012-03-16 | publisher = BBC | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120316235037/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-17410374 | archive-date = 2012-03-16 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。游戏音频网络协会（Game Audio Network Guild）向《传送门2》授予了“最佳对话”、“最佳交互作曲”和“最佳原声”（针对游戏主题曲《Want You Gone》）三个奖项<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/165833/Battlefield_3_Portal_2_more_win_big_at_10th_annual_GANG_Awards.php | title = Battlefield 3, Portal 2, more win big at 10th annual G.A.N.G. Awards | first = Tom | last = Curtis | date = 2012-03-14 | accessdate = 2012-03-14 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120317172318/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/165833/Battlefield_3_Portal_2_more_win_big_at_10th_annual_GANG_Awards.php | archive-date = 2012-03-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在纽约游戏评论家圈子奖（New York Videogame Critics Circle Awards）首次颁奖中，《传送门2》获得了最佳编剧和最佳表演的荣誉<ref>{{cite web | url = http://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/02/03/skyrim-wins-video-game-critics-award/ | title = Skyrim Wins Video Game Critics Award | first = Seth | last = Schiesel | date = 2012-02-03 | accessdate = 2012-02-07 | work = [[纽约时报|New York Times]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120207034033/http://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/02/03/skyrim-wins-video-game-critics-award/ | archive-date = 2012-02-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在2012年的[[金摇杆奖|金摇杆奖]]中，“永久测试行动计划”获得了“最佳DLC”奖项<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.vg247.com/2012/10/26/winners-of-the-2012-golden-joystick-awards-announced/ | title = 2012 Golden Joystick Awards – Skyrim wins Ultimate Game of the Year | publisher = [[VG247|VG247]] | first = Stephany | last = Nunneley | date = 2012-10-26 | accessdate = 2012-10-26 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/6COi2VIhJ?url=http://www.vg247.com/2012/10/26/winners-of-the-2012-golden-joystick-awards-announced/ | archive-date = 2012-11-23 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2016年底，《傳送門2》入圍了由社群票選的第一屆[[Steam大獎|Steam大獎]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.pcgamer.com/valve-reveals-steam-awards-nominees/|title=Valve reveals Steam Awards nominees|work=PC Gamer|access-date=2018-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612143809/https://www.pcgamer.com/valve-reveals-steam-awards-nominees/|archive-date=2018-06-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並贏得「最需要抱抱的壞人」（Villain Most In Need Of A Hug）類別的勝利<ref>{{cite web|url=https://store.steampowered.com/SteamAwards/2016|title=The Steam Awards|website=Steam|access-date=2018-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612150328/https://store.steampowered.com/SteamAwards/2016|archive-date=2018-06-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 销售情况 ===
基于[[亚马逊公司|亚马逊公司]]给出的销售数据，可以得知《传送门2》在发售的第一周就成为了美国最畅销的游戏<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/34245/Saling_The_World_Portal_2_Leads_CrossPlatform_Charts_Worldwide.php | title = Saling The World: ''Portal 2'' Leads Cross-Platform Charts Worldwide | first = Danny | last = Cowen | date = 2011-04-22 | accessdate = 2011-06-27 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110508225028/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/34245/Saling_The_World_Portal_2_Leads_CrossPlatform_Charts_Worldwide.php | archive-date = 2011-05-08 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但在第二周被新版的《[[真人快打系列|真人快打]]》所超越<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/34356/Saling_The_World_Mortal_Kombat_Overtakes_Portal_2_Stateside.php | title = Saling The World: Mortal Kombat Overtakes Portal 2 Stateside | first = Danny | last = Cowen | date = 2011-04-29 | accessdate = 2011-04-29 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110430220720/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/34356/Saling_The_World_Mortal_Kombat_Overtakes_Portal_2_Stateside.php | archive-date = 2011-04-30 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。根据[[NPD集团|NPD集团]]的调研情况，《传送门2》在2011年4月美国游戏销量中名列第二（约637,000份）<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-05-12-npd-mortal-kombat-beats-portal-2-in-us | title = NPD: Mortal Kombat beats Portal 2 in US | first = Fred | last = Dutton | date = 2011-05-12 | accessdate = 2011-06-27 | publisher = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110517205317/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-05-12-npd-mortal-kombat-beats-portal-2-in-us | archive-date = 2011-05-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，并在5月排名第四<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/35201/NPD_May_US_Retail_Game_Industry_Sales_Lowest_Since_Oct_06.php | title = NPD: May U.S. Retail Game Industry Sales Lowest Since Oct. '06 | first = Kris | last = Graft | date = 2001-06-13 | accessdate = 2011-06-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110617062130/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/35201/NPD_May_US_Retail_Game_Industry_Sales_Lowest_Since_Oct_06.php | archive-date = 2011-06-17 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。然而，NPD集团的数据并不包括Steam平台上的销量<ref name="giant bomb 3m">{{cite web | url = http://www.giantbomb.com/news/portal-2-has-sold-more-than-3-million-copies/3412/ | title = Portal 2 Has Sold More Than 3 Million Copies | first = Patrick | last = Klepek | date = 2011-06-22 | accessdate = 2014-12-16 | publisher = [[Giant_Bomb|Giant Bomb]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121018222444/http://www.giantbomb.com/news/portal-2-has-sold-more-than-3-million-copies/3412/ | archive-date = 2012-10-18 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在英国，《传送门2》在发售首周销量就排名第一<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/34287/Portal_2_Scores_Valve_First_Ever_Top_Spot_In_UK_Sales_Charts.php | title = Portal 2 Scores Valve First Ever Top Spot In UK Sales Charts | first = Mike | last = Rose | date = 2011-04-26 | accessdate = 2011-04-26 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110429021926/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/34287/Portal_2_Scores_Valve_First_Ever_Top_Spot_In_UK_Sales_Charts.php | archive-date = 2011-04-29 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，第二周继续保持第一<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/34468/Portal_2_Holds_On_To_Top_Spot_For_Second_Week_In_UK_Sales_Charts.php | title = Portal 2 Holds On To Top Spot For Second Week In UK Sales Charts | first = Mike | last = Rose | date = 2011-05-03 | accessdate = 2011-05-03 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110506054314/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/34468/Portal_2_Holds_On_To_Top_Spot_For_Second_Week_In_UK_Sales_Charts.php | archive-date = 2011-05-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

《传送门2》在PlayStation Network发生大规模故障的前几天发售。[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]的分析师马特·马修斯（Matt Matthews）基于NPD集团的数据进行分析，认为此次故障“没有严重影响软件的零售销量”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/35290 | title = Analysis: Did The PSN Outage Hurt U.S. PS3 Hardware Sales? | first = Matt | last = Matthews | publisher = Gamasutra | date = 2011-06-21 | accessdate = 2011-06-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141011072659/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/35290 | archive-date = 2014-10-11 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但是一些开发商指出他们的销售额确实出现了下降<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/34306/Developers_Say_PSN_Outage_Affecting_Sales_But_Remain_Hopeful.php | title = Developers Say PSN Outage Affecting Sales, But Remain Hopeful | first = Kris | last = Graft | publisher = Gamasutra | date = 2001-04-26 | accessdate = 2011-06-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110811064726/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/34306/Developers_Say_PSN_Outage_Affecting_Sales_But_Remain_Hopeful.php | archive-date = 2011-08-11 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。ShopToNews分析师乔·安德森（Joe Anderson）估计故障不会给《传送门2》在英国的销售带来太大影响<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.shoptonews.net/2011/04/26/has-psn-outage-affected-portal-2-ps3-sales/ | title = Has PSN outage affected Portal 2 PS3 sales? | first = Joe | last = Anderson | publisher = ShopToNews | date = 2011-04-26 | accessdate = 2011-06-27 | archivedate = 2012-05-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120512200042/http://www.shoptonews.net/2011/04/26/has-psn-outage-affected-portal-2-ps3-sales/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2011年6月22日，加布·纽维尔宣布《传送门2》已经售出300万份<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/35402/Newell_Portal_2_Has_Sold_3_Million_Copies.php | title = Newell: Portal 2 Has Sold 3 Million Copies | first = Kyle | last = Orland | date = 2011-06-22 | accessdate = 2011-06-22 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110625134506/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/35402/Newell_Portal_2_Has_Sold_3_Million_Copies.php | archive-date = 2011-06-25 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。截至7月，美国艺电表示全球各地的零售商已售出超过200万份的《传送门2》<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-07-26-crysis-2-racks-up-three-million-sales | title = Crysis 2 racks up three million sales | publisher = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | date = 2011-07-26 | accessdate = 2011-07-26 | first = Fred | last = Dutton | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110807062713/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-07-26-crysis-2-racks-up-three-million-sales | archive-date = 2011-08-07 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。加布·纽维尔在8月接受采访时说，“《传送门2》在PC上比在游戏机上做得更好”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/6471/the_valve_way_gabe_newell_and_.php?page=4 | title = The Valve Way: Gabe Newell And Erik Johnson Speak | first = Christian | last = Nutt | date = 2011-08-29 | accessdate = 2011-08-30 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110930134908/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/6471/the_valve_way_gabe_newell_and_.php?page=4 | archive-date = 2011-09-30 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2012年5月，“永久测试行动计划”放出时，纽厄尔称传送门销售量已超过400万，而且个人电脑的销量超过了游戏机。总体而言，《传送门》和《传送门2》总共售出了超过800万份<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/169967/Portal_2_has_sold_over_4M_copies.php | title = Portal 2 has sold over 4M copies | first = Eric | last = Caoili | date = 2012-05-08 | accessdate = 2012-05-08 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120508191845/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/169967/Portal_2_has_sold_over_4M_copies.php | archive-date = 2012-05-08 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 模組 ==
{{see also|{{tsl|en|List of Source mods|Source模組列表}}}}
除了玩家設計的關卡之外，還有一些由玩家製作的完整《傳送門2》[[模組|模組]]。
=== 《傳送門故事：梅爾》 ===

{{Main|傳送門故事：梅爾}}
單人模組，由8名傳送門系列粉絲組成的Prism Studios開發，於2015年6月25日發布，支援Windows、OS X和Linux系統，在Steam上擁有《傳送門2》的玩家可以免費取得<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2015/01/31/fan-made-portal-2-mod-looks-good-enough-to-be-from-valve.aspx | title = Fan Made Portal 2 Mod Looks Good Enough To Be From Valve | first = Kyle | last = Hillard | date = 2015-01-31 | accessdate = 2015-05-10 | work = [[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] | dead-url = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150702043017/http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2015/01/31/fan-made-portal-2-mod-looks-good-enough-to-be-from-valve.aspx | archivedate = 2015-07-02 }}</ref>。

=== 《光圈凝膠》 ===
{{Main|光圈凝膠}}
單人模組，由「The Aperture Tag Team」開發，於2014年發行。在此模組中，「凝膠槍」取代了「傳送門槍」，可以射出和《傳送門2》裡面一樣的凝膠<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.pcgamer.com/portal-2-mod-aperture-tag-releases-on-steam-for-a-price/ | title = Portal 2 mod Aperture Tag releases on Steam, for a price | first = Phil | last = Savage | date = 2014-07-16 | accessdate = 2019-05-27 | work = [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190527231908/https://www.pcgamer.com/portal-2-mod-aperture-tag-releases-on-steam-for-a-price/ | archive-date = 2019-05-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 《传送门：时间机器》 ===
{{Main|{{tsl|en|Thinking with Time Machine|传送门：时间机器}}}}
單人模組，由魯斯蘭·雷布卡（{{lang|en|Ruslan Rybka}}）開發，於2014年發行。當中，玩家可以重新讀取之前的行動，由玩家角色的複製人演示出來<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.pcgamer.com/portal-2-mod-thinking-with-time-machine-now-available-on-steam/ | title = Portal 2 mod Thinking With Time Machine now available on Steam | date = 2014-04-22 | accessdate = 2019-05-27 | work = [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190527231220/https://www.pcgamer.com/portal-2-mod-thinking-with-time-machine-now-available-on-steam/ | archive-date = 2019-05-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.wired.com/2014/04/thinking-with-time-machine/ | title = This Portal 2 Mod Lets You Play Against Yourself | first = Bo | last = Moore | date = 2014-04-28 | accessdate = 2019-05-27 | work = [[Wired_(magazine)|Wired]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150518090329/http://www.wired.com/2014/04/thinking-with-time-machine/ | archive-date = 2015-05-18 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 《Portal Reloaded》 ===
單人模組，由「PORTANIS」開發，於2021年發行。此模組新增具備時空穿越能力的「綠色傳送門」，可讓玩家在「目前」和二十年後的「未來」兩個時間線進行遊戲。

